  "detailed_description": "Neon Warrior is an action game with side view and puzzles.<br><br>You will take on the role of a hero and make a journey full of dangers in a fantastic neon world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505440/extras/28b96807fc568396cd2fbc94bd45f0a0.avif?t=1658215840\" width=610 height=441 /></span><br>Main features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>It will appeal to both beginners and seasoned gamers.<br></li><li>Interesting achievements for completing levels.<br></li><li>Atmospheric music.<br></li><li>Endless rounds of ammunition.</li></ul>",
